# Cite Creator Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.
<br /><br />
The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/), and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [2.0.0] - 2024-07-01

### Added

- Added prettier for code formatting
- Added eslint for linting
- Automated testing with puppeteer
- More positioning options for cite box
- Configurable keyboard shortcuts and better defaults for mac compatibility
- Support for multiline cites, even though they're not advised
- Automated build script for packaging extension for each browser store
- Option to split first/last name in custom cite formats
- Made cite box minimizable
- Option to use slashes instead of dashes in date format
- Debug mode for logging to console

### Changed

- Updated manifest.json to version 3
- Updated extension to work cross-browser with the web-ext polyfill
- Refactored the majority of the code to be more modular, handle state management better, etc.
- Updated icons to a better color for cross-browser use, and added icon sizes for different locations
- Switched to modern hotkeys library for keyboard shortcuts, removed mousetrap.js
- Replaced date.js with native date functions
- Made the version string on the options page dynamic
- Cite box now reloads automatically whenever options change

## [1.1.1] 2016-03-25

### Changed

- Last version before being put under version control, minor changes from original.
